business_definition: Main record structure for date conversion processing containing input specifications, output specifications, and error messaging
Input record group containing the date format type indicator and the input date value to be converted
Input date format type indicator specifying the format of the incoming date
Condition indicating input date is in YYYYMMDD format without separators (VALUE "1")
Condition indicating input date is in YYYY-MM-DD format with dash separators (VALUE "2")
Input date field containing the date value to be converted in various possible formats
Redefined structure for parsing YYYYMMDD format input date (REDEFINES CODATECN-INP-DATE)
Four-digit year component extracted from YYYYMMDD format input date
Two-digit month component extracted from YYYYMMDD format input date
Two-digit day component extracted from YYYYMMDD format input date
Unused trailing portion of input date field for YYYYMMDD format
Redefined structure for parsing YYYY-MM-DD format input date with separators (REDEFINES CODATECN-INP-DATE)
Four-digit year component for YYYY-MM-DD formatted output date
First separator character between year and month in formatted input date
Second separator character between month and day in formatted input date
Two-digit day component extracted from YYYY-MM-DD format input date
Unused trailing portion of input date field for YYYY-MM-DD format
Output record group containing the converted date format type indicator and the converted date value
Output date format type indicator specifying the desired format for the converted date
Condition indicating output date should be in YYYY-MM-DD format with dash separators (VALUE "1")
Condition indicating output date should be in YYYYMMDD format without separators (VALUE "2")
Output date field containing the converted date value in the requested format
Redefined structure for formatting output date in YYYY-MM-DD format with separators (REDEFINES CODATECN-0UT-DATE)
First separator character between year and month in formatted output date
Two-digit month component for YYYY-MM-DD formatted output date
Second separator character between month and day in formatted output date
Two-digit day component for YYYY-MM-DD formatted output date
Redefined structure for formatting output date in YYYYMMDD format without separators (REDEFINES CODATECN-0UT-DATE)
Four-digit year component for YYYYMMDD formatted output date
Two-digit month component for YYYYMMDD formatted output date
Two-digit day component for YYYYMMDD formatted output date
Error message field containing descriptive text when date conversion processing encounters an error
